Robert T. Worthington  COO, SVP, General Counsel and Secretary , Mercantile Bank CorporationAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 0 Board Members in 0 different organizations across 2 different industries.42$318,396As of Fiscal Year 2016
Background

		Mr. Robert T. Worthington has been Chief Operating Officer and Company Secretary of Mercantile Bank Corp. since January 1, 2017 and has been its Senior Vice President and General Counsel since June 15, 2016. Mr. Worthington has been Senior Vice President of Mercantile Bank of Michigan since November 2009 and has been its General Counsel since 2011. He has been Chief Operating Officer of Mercantile Bank of Michigan since January 2016 and has been its Secretary since January ... 1, 2017 served as its Risk Management Director since November 2009. Mr. Worthington has 22 years of banking and corporate finance experience. He joined Mercantile Bank of Michigan in 2009. Prior to joining Mercantile Bank of Michigan, he served as a corporate attorney, internal auditor, certified public accountant and bank teller. Mr. Worthington serves as Chairman of Junior Achievement of the Michigan Great Lakes, Committee Member of the Gerald R. Ford Presidential Foundation, Trustee of the Michigan Bankers Workers Compensation Fund, Director of MiBankPAC and Chairman of the Michigan Bankers Association’s Grassroots Advocacy Committee.Read Full Background




