Robert T. Worthington

Public asset : 645,749 USDLinked companies :  Mercantile Bank Corp. 





Summary 



Mr. Robert T. Worthington is Chairman at Junior Achievement of The Michigan Great Lakes, COO, Secretary, General Counsel & Senior VP at Mercantile Bank Corp. and COO, Secretary, General Counsel & Senior VP at Mercantile Bank of Michigan.He is on the Board of Directors at Michigan Bankers Association and Michigan Bankers Workers Compensation Fund. Mr. Worthington also served on the board at Federal Home Loan Bank of Indianapolis.



